{"type":"message","id":"75ddb956","parentId":"93ace299","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:03:50.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，报告已经生成。现在我需要：\n1. 更新 evolution-history（创建一个新的 round 记录）\n2. 检查 pattern-registry 是否需要更新\n\n让我先创建一个新的 evolution round 记录，然后检查 pattern-registry。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4eb7cd6ab13646718a654f66","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-187-2026-02-25-0400.md","content":"# Evolution Round 187 - 2026-02-25 04:00\n\n## 类型\n日志深度分析 (evolver-log-analysis)\n\n## 发现的问题\n\n### P0 - 高频 API Rate Limit\n- **问题**: GLM-5 模型 429 错误频发\n- **数据**: 91 次错误（15.2/h），峰值 08:00（38 次）\n- **影响**: 任务执行中断，系统效率下降\n\n### P1 - 工具调用失败\n- **file_not_found**: 20 次\n- **edit_not_found**: 8 次\n- **影响**: 文件操作失败，需要重试\n\n### P2 - 配置缺失\n- **Brave API Key**: 未配置\n- **影响**: web_search 功能不可用\n\n## 改进建议\n\n1. **实现指数退避重试机制** (P0)\n   - 检测到 429 时自动退避\n   - 最大重试 3 次，延迟 1s→2s→4s\n\n2. **错峰调度** (P0)\n   - 调整 cron 任务时间\n   - 避免 07:00-09:00 高峰期重叠\n\n3. **文件操作前置检查** (P1)\n   - read 前检查文件存在\n   - edit 失败时提供更友好提示\n\n## 系统状态\n\n| 指标 | 值 | 趋势 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| 健康度 | 7.5/10 | ⬇️ |\n| 429 错误率 | 15.2/h | ⬆️ |\n| 任务成功率 | ~95% | ➡️ |\n\n## 下一步\n\n- [ ] 实现退避机制\n- [ ] 调整 cron 调度\n- [ ] 配置 Brave API Key\n\n---\n*Generated by evolver-log-analysis*\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d70916e32a154f34afd788dc","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2268,"output":551,"cacheRead":72064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771963407455}}
