{"type":"message","id":"de709eba","parentId":"0f5c3cd1","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:30:01.596Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 4:30 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771965001589}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9065b37","parentId":"de709eba","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:30:56.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次要求执行深度日志分析任务。上次分析是在 04:00，现在是 04:30，已经过去了 30 分钟。\n\n让我进行新的深度分析，看看这 30 分钟内是否有新的问题或变化。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_54ee220f23af420685089225","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/deep_analysis_0430.js << 'SCRIPT'\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst sessionsDir = '/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions';\nconst sixHoursAgo = Date.now() - (6 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst thirtyMinAgo = Date.now() - (30 * 60 * 1000);\n\nconst results = {\n  scanTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  files: 0,\n  lines: 0,\n  last30m: { lines: 0, errors: 0, tasks: {} },\n  last6h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0, api4xx: 0 }, tasks: {}, hourly: {} },\n  toolFailures: { file_not_found: 0, edit_not_found: 0, other: 0 },\n  configErrors: 0,\n  connectionErrors: 0,\n  patterns: []\n};\n\nconst files = fs.readdirSync(sessionsDir)\n  .filter(f => f.endsWith('.jsonl'))\n  .map(f => ({\n    name: f,\n    path: path.join(sessionsDir, f),\n    mtime: fs.statSync(path.join(sessionsDir, f)).mtime.getTime()\n  }))\n  .filter(f => f.mtime >= sixHoursAgo)\n  .sort((a, b) => b.mtime - a.mtime);\n\nresults.files = files.length;\n\nconsole.log('=== Deep Log Analysis (04:30) ===');\nconsole.log(`Time: ${results.scanTime}`);\nconsole.log(`Files in last 6h: ${files.length}\\n`);\n\nlet consecutive429 = 0;\nlet maxConsecutive429 = 0;\nlet lastWas429 = false;\nlet last429Time = null;\nlet gapAnalysis = [];\n\nfiles.forEach(file => {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(file.path, 'utf8');\n  const lines = content.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());\n  results.lines += lines.length;\n  \n  lines.forEach(line => {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(line);\n      const timestamp = data.timestamp;\n      const lineTime = new Date(timestamp).getTime();\n      const hour = timestamp ? timestamp.substring(11, 13) : 'unknown';\n      \n      if (!results.last6h.hourly[hour]) {\n        results.last6h.hourly[hour] = { errors: 0, messages: 0 };\n      }\n      results.last6h.hourly[hour].messages++;\n      \n      // Last 30 min stats\n      if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n        results.last30m.lines++;\n      }\n      \n      // Task tracking\n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'user') {\n        const match = JSON.stringify(data.message.content).match(/\\[cron:[^\\s]+\\s+([^\\]]+)\\]/);\n        if (match) {\n          results.last6h.tasks[match[1]] = (results.last6h.tasks[match[1]] || 0) + 1;\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n            results.last30m.tasks[match[1]] = (results.last30m.tasks[match[1]] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Error analysis\n      if (data.message?.stopReason === 'error') {\n        const errorMsg = data.message.errorMessage || '';\n        results.last6h.hourly[hour].errors++;\n        \n        if (errorMsg.includes('429') || errorMsg.includes('速率限制') || errorMsg.includes('访问量过大')) {\n          results.last6h.errors.api429++;\n          \n          // Track consecutive 429s\n          if (lastWas429 && last429Time) {\n            const gap = lineTime - last429Time;\n            gapAnalysis.push(gap);\n          }\n          \n          if (lastWas429) {\n            consecutive429++;\n            maxConsecutive429 = Math.max(maxConsecutive429, consecutive429);\n          } else {\n            consecutive429 = 1;\n          }\n          lastWas429 = true;\n          last429Time = lineTime;\n          \n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n            results.last30m.errors++;\n          }\n        } else {\n          lastWas429 = false;\n          consecutive429 = 0;\n        }\n        \n        if (errorMsg.includes('500') || errorMsg.includes('502') || errorMsg.includes('503')) {\n          results.last6h.errors.api5xx++;\n        }\n        if (errorMsg.includes('400') || errorMsg.includes('参数有误')) {\n          results.last6h.errors.api4xx++;\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Tool failures\n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'toolResult') {\n        const resultStr = JSON.stringify(data.message.content);\n        \n        if (resultStr.includes('error') || resultStr.includes('Error')) {\n          if (resultStr.includes('ENOENT') || resultStr.includes('no such file')) {\n            results.toolFailures.file_not_found++;\n          } else if (resultStr.includes('Could not find the exact text')) {\n            results.toolFailures.edit_not_found++;\n          } else if (resultStr.includes('missing_brave_api_key')) {\n            results.configErrors++;\n          } else if (resultStr.includes('ECONNREFUSED') || resultStr.includes('ETIMEDOUT')) {\n            results.connectionErrors++;\n          } else {\n            results.toolFailures.other++;\n          }\n        }\n      }\n      \n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n});\n\n// Calculate average gap between 429s\nconst avgGap = gapAnalysis.length > 0 \n  ? (gapAnalysis.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0) / gapAnalysis.length / 1000).toFixed(1)\n  : 0;\n\nconsole.log('=== Summary ===\\n');\nconsole.log(`Total files: ${results.files}`);\nconsole.log(`Total lines: ${results.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 30 min lines: ${results.last30m.lines}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== API Errors (6h) ===');\nconsole.log(`429 Rate Limit: ${results.last6h.errors.api429} (${(results.last6h.errors.api429/6).toFixed(1)}/hour)`);\nconsole.log(`5xx Server Error: ${results.last6h.errors.api5xx}`);\nconsole.log(`4xx Client Error: ${results.last6h.errors.api4xx}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Last 30 Minutes ===');\nconsole.log(`Messages: ${results.last30m.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`429 Errors: ${results.last30m.errors}`);\nconsole.log(`Tasks: ${Object.keys(results.last30m.tasks).length}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Tool Failures ===');\nconsole.log(`file_not_found: ${results.toolFailures.file_not_found}`);\nconsole.log(`edit_not_found: ${results.toolFailures.edit_not_found}`);\nconsole.log(`other: ${results.toolFailures.other}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== 429 Pattern Analysis ===');\nconsole.log(`Max consecutive: ${maxConsecutive429}`);\nconsole.log(`Avg gap between 429s: ${avgGap}s\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Hourly Error Distribution ===');\nObject.entries(results.last6h.hourly)\n  .filter(([h, d]) => d.errors > 0)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1].errors - a[1].errors)\n  .slice(0, 8)\n  .forEach(([hour, data]) => {\n    console.log(`${hour}:00 - ${data.errors} errors`);\n  });\n\nconsole.log('\\n=== Top Tasks (6h) ===');\nObject.entries(results.last6h.tasks)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1])\n  .slice(0, 8)\n  .forEach(([task, count]) => {\n    console.log(`${task}: ${count} runs`);\n  });\n\n// Health score calculation\nconst errorRate = results.last6h.errors.api429 / 6;\nlet healthScore = 10;\nif (errorRate > 10) healthScore -= 2;\nif (errorRate > 15) healthScore -= 1;\nif (errorRate > 20) healthScore -= 1;\nif (results.toolFailures.file_not_found > 15) healthScore -= 0.5;\n\nconsole.log(`\\n=== Health Score: ${healthScore}/10 ===`);\n\nfs.writeFileSync('/tmp/analysis_0430.json', JSON.stringify(results, null, 2));\nconsole.log('\\nResults saved to /tmp/analysis_0430.json');\nSCRIPT\n\nnode /tmp/deep_analysis_0430.js","timeout":120,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":66502,"output":1928,"cacheRead":10560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78990,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771965001592}}
