{"type":"message","id":"8273523e","parentId":"ab8ae5f8","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:33:42.156Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，分析完成。让我总结一下结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 深度日志分析完成 (04:30)\n\n### 分析结果\n\n| 指标 | 数值 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Session 文件 | 22 个 | ✅ |\n| 消息行数 | 4,447 | ✅ |\n| 最近 30 分钟 429 | **0** | ✅ 稳定 |\n| 6 小时 429 总数 | 91 (15.2/h) | ⚠️ |\n\n### 关键发现\n\n1. **当前稳定**: 最近 30 分钟 **0 次 429 错误**\n2. **时段聚集**: 429 错误集中在 **07:00-09:00**（占 73%）\n3. **统计修正**: 真实工具错误为 0（之前误将 exec 输出判为错误）\n\n### 健康评分: 7/10 ⚠️\n\n**下降原因**: 持续的 429 错误累积影响（主要是高峰期）\n\n### 生成的文件\n\n- ✅ 报告: `memory/log-analysis-2026-02-25-0430.md`\n- ✅ Round: `evolver_history/.../round-188-2026-02-25-0430.md`\n- ✅ Pattern: 更新 PAT-018（高峰期 429 爆发）\n\n### 立即行动建议\n\n| 优先级 | 行动 | 预期效果 |\n|--------|------|----------|\n| **P0** | 错峰调度（避开 07:00-09:00） | 减少 70% 高峰错误 |\n| P1 | 混沌代理 27/h → 15/h | 降低整体负载 |\n| P2 | 添加 5 秒请求间隔 | 防止突发请求 |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":219,"output":421,"cacheRead":86848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87488,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771965205173}}
{"type":"message","id":"86939641","parentId":"8273523e","timestamp":"2026-02-24T21:00:00.528Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 5:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771966800524}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d3c69cd","parentId":"86939641","timestamp":"2026-02-24T21:00:51.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我执行深度日志分析任务。上次分析是 04:30，现在是 05:00，间隔 30 分钟。\n\n我需要：\n1. 分析最近 6 小时的日志\n2. 找出错误模式、性能问题、API 问题、配置问题、流程问题\n3. 生成报告文件\n4. 更新 evolution-history\n5. 如果有新模式，更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n让我开始分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c87e7a9ae4e74424abde1fd6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/deep_analysis_0500.js << 'SCRIPT'\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst sessionsDir = '/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions';\nconst sixHoursAgo = Date.now() - (6 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst oneHourAgo = Date.now() - (60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst thirtyMinAgo = Date.now() - (30 * 60 * 1000);\n\nconst results = {\n  scanTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  files: 0,\n  lines: 0,\n  periods: {\n    last6h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0, api4xx: 0 }, tasks: {}, hourly: {} },\n    last1h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0 }, tasks: {} },\n    last30m: { errors: 0, tasks: {}, lines: 0 }\n  },\n  patterns: {\n    consecutive429: 0,\n    maxConsecutive429: 0,\n    peakHours: []\n  },\n  toolErrors: { fileNotFound: 0, editNotFound: 0, other: 0 },\n  processErrors: 0\n};\n\nconst files = fs.readdirSync(sessionsDir)\n  .filter(f => f.endsWith('.jsonl'))\n  .map(f => ({\n    path: path.join(sessionsDir, f),\n    mtime: fs.statSync(path.join(sessionsDir, f)).mtime.getTime()\n  }))\n  .filter(f => f.mtime >= sixHoursAgo);\n\nresults.files = files.length;\n\nlet lastWas429 = false;\nlet consecutive429 = 0;\n\nfiles.forEach(file => {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(file.path, 'utf8');\n  const lines = content.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());\n  results.lines += lines.length;\n  \n  lines.forEach(line => {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(line);\n      const timestamp = data.timestamp;\n      const lineTime = new Date(timestamp).getTime();\n      const hour = timestamp ? timestamp.substring(11, 13) : 'unknown';\n      \n      // Hourly distribution\n      if (!results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour]) {\n        results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour] = { errors: 0, messages: 0 };\n      }\n      results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].messages++;\n      \n      // 30 min stats\n      if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n        results.periods.last30m.lines++;\n      }\n      \n      // Task tracking\n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'user') {\n        const match = JSON.stringify(data.message.content).match(/\\[cron:[^\\s]+\\s+([^\\]]+)\\]/);\n        if (match) {\n          const task = match[1];\n          results.periods.last6h.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last6h.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          \n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) {\n            results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n            results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Error analysis\n      if (data.message?.stopReason === 'error') {\n        const errorMsg = data.message.errorMessage || '';\n        results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].errors++;\n        \n        // 429 errors\n        if (errorMsg.includes('429') || errorMsg.includes('速率限制') || errorMsg.includes('访问量过大')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api429++;\n          \n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) {\n            results.periods.last1h.errors.api429++;\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n            results.periods.last30m.errors++;\n          }\n          \n          // Consecutive tracking\n          if (lastWas429) {\n            consecutive429++;\n            results.patterns.maxConsecutive429 = Math.max(results.patterns.maxConsecutive429, consecutive429);\n          } else {\n            consecutive429 = 1;\n          }\n          lastWas429 = true;\n        } else {\n          lastWas429 = false;\n          consecutive429 = 0;\n        }\n        \n        // 5xx errors\n        if (errorMsg.includes('500') || errorMsg.includes('502') || errorMsg.includes('503')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api5xx++;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) results.periods.last1h.errors.api5xx++;\n        }\n        \n        // 4xx errors\n        if (errorMsg.includes('400') || errorMsg.includes('参数有误')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api4xx++;\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Process errors\n      if (data.type === 'custom' && data.customType?.includes('error')) {\n        results.processErrors++;\n      }\n      \n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n});\n\n// Find peak hours\nresults.patterns.peakHours = Object.entries(results.periods.last6h.hourly)\n  .filter(([h, d]) => d.errors > 5)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1].errors - a[1].errors)\n  .map(([h, d]) => ({ hour: h, errors: d.errors }));\n\nconsole.log('=== Deep Log Analysis (05:00) ===');\nconsole.log(`Time: ${results.scanTime}`);\nconsole.log(`Files: ${results.files}, Lines: ${results.lines}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== 6 Hour Summary ===');\nconsole.log(`429: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api429} (${(results.periods.last6h.errors.api429/6).toFixed(1)}/h)`);\nconsole.log(`5xx: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api5xx}`);\nconsole.log(`4xx: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api4xx}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Last 1 Hour ===');\nconsole.log(`429: ${results.periods.last1h.errors.api429}`);\nconsole.log(`5xx: ${results.periods.last1h.errors.api5xx}`);\nconsole.log(`Tasks: ${Object.keys(results.periods.last1h.tasks).length}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Last 30 Minutes ===');\nconsole.log(`Lines: ${results.periods.last30m.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`429 Errors: ${results.periods.last30m.errors}`);\nconsole.log(`Active Tasks: ${Object.keys(results.periods.last30m.tasks).length}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Peak Hours (errors > 5) ===');\nresults.patterns.peakHours.forEach(p => {\n  console.log(`  ${p.hour}:00 - ${p.errors} errors`);\n});\n\nconsole.log('\\n=== Top Tasks (6h → 1h → 30m) ===');\nObject.entries(results.periods.last6h.tasks)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1])\n  .slice(0, 8)\n  .forEach(([task, count6h]) => {\n    const count1h = results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] || 0;\n    const count30m = results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] || 0;\n    console.log(`  ${task}: ${count6h} → ${count1h}/h → ${count30m}/30m`);\n  });\n\n// Health score\nconst rate6h = results.periods.last6h.errors.api429 / 6;\nconst rate1h = results.periods.last1h.errors.api429;\nlet health = 10;\nif (rate6h > 10) health -= 2;\nif (rate6h > 15) health -= 1;\nif (rate1h > 3) health -= 1;\nif (results.periods.last30m.errors > 0) health -= 1;\nif (rate1h === 0 && rate6h > 10) health += 0.5; // recovering\n\nconsole.log(`\\n=== Health Score: ${health}/10 ===`);\n\n// Trend analysis\nconsole.log('\\n=== Trend Analysis ===');\nconsole.log(`6h rate: ${rate6h.toFixed(1)}/h`);\nconsole.log(`1h rate: ${rate1h}/h`);\nif (rate1h < rate6h) {\n  console.log('✅ Improving - error rate decreasing');\n} else if (rate1h > rate6h) {\n  console.log('⚠️ Worsening - error rate increasing');\n} else {\n  console.log('➡️ Stable');\n}\n\nfs.writeFileSync('/tmp/analysis_0500.json', JSON.stringify(results, null, 2));\nSCRIPT\n\nnode /tmp/deep_analysis_0500.js","timeout":120,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":81851,"output":2057,"cacheRead":5632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771966800526}}
