{"type":"message","id":"6766cf40","parentId":"84192b50","timestamp":"2026-02-24T21:02:31.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"分析完成！总结一下：\n\n1. ✅ 生成了报告文件: memory/log-analysis-2026-02-25-0500.md\n2. ✅ 更新了 evolution-history: round-189-2026-02-25-0500.md\n3. ✅ 更新了 pattern-registry.md: PAT-018 状态改为\"已恢复\"，健康评分更新为 7.5/10\n\n关键发现：\n- 系统已恢复，最近 1 小时 429 错误为 0\n- 健康评分从 7/10 恢复到 7.5/10\n- 趋势分析显示系统正在改善","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 深度日志分析完成 (05:00)\n\n### 关键发现\n\n| 指标 | 数值 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 6h 429 错误 | 91 (15.2/h) | ⚠️ 历史问题 |\n| **1h 429 错误** | **0** | ✅ **完美** |\n| **30m 429 错误** | **0** | ✅ **稳定** |\n| 健康评分 | **7.5/10** | ⬆️ 恢复中 |\n\n### 🎉 系统已恢复\n\n**趋势分析**:\n```\n6h 平均: 15.2/h (历史高)\n1h:      0/h    ✅ 完美\n30m:     0/h    ✅ 稳定\n```\n\n**恢复时间线**:\n- 07:00-09:00: 高峰期错误爆发（72 次）\n- 10:00-05:00: 系统稳定恢复（0 次）\n\n### 生成的文件\n\n- ✅ 报告: `memory/log-analysis-2026-02-25-0500.md`\n- ✅ Round: `evolver_history/.../round-189-2026-02-25-0500.md`\n- ✅ Pattern: PAT-018 更新为 **✅已恢复**\n\n### 健康评分趋势\n\n```\n04:00 → 7.5/10\n04:30 → 7.0/10\n05:00 → 7.5/10 ✅ (恢复中)\n```\n\n### 建议行动\n\n1. ✅ 系统恢复已确认\n2. 🔧 **预防措施**: 实施错峰调度，避免下一个 07:00-09:00 高峰期"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":468,"output":566,"cacheRead":93440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94474,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771966933674}}
{"type":"message","id":"bca8c65d","parentId":"6766cf40","timestamp":"2026-02-24T21:54:01.428Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 5:54 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771970041424}}
{"type":"message","id":"c21a9ed6","parentId":"bca8c65d","timestamp":"2026-02-24T21:54:49.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行深度日志分析任务。当前时间是 2026-02-25 05:54。让我分析最近 6 小时的日志，特别关注错误模式、性能问题、API 问题等。\n\n我需要：\n1. 读取 session 日志\n2. 分析错误模式\n3. 生成报告文件\n4. 更新 evolution history\n5. 如有新模式，更新 pattern-registry.md","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e06f75ca00bd4d0586f209d1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/deep_analysis_0554.js << 'SCRIPT'\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst sessionsDir = '/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions';\nconst sixHoursAgo = Date.now() - (6 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst oneHourAgo = Date.now() - (60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst thirtyMinAgo = Date.now() - (30 * 60 * 1000);\n\nconst results = {\n  scanTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  files: 0,\n  lines: 0,\n  periods: {\n    last6h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0, api4xx: 0 }, tasks: {}, hourly: {} },\n    last1h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0 }, tasks: {} },\n    last30m: { errors: 0, tasks: {}, lines: 0 }\n  },\n  patterns: {\n    consecutive429: 0,\n    maxConsecutive429: 0,\n    peakHours: []\n  },\n  toolErrors: [],\n  processErrors: 0,\n  newPatterns: []\n};\n\nconst files = fs.readdirSync(sessionsDir)\n  .filter(f => f.endsWith('.jsonl'))\n  .map(f => ({\n    path: path.join(sessionsDir, f),\n    mtime: fs.statSync(path.join(sessionsDir, f)).mtime.getTime()\n  }))\n  .filter(f => f.mtime >= sixHoursAgo);\n\nresults.files = files.length;\n\nlet lastWas429 = false;\nlet consecutive429 = 0;\n\nfiles.forEach(file => {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(file.path, 'utf8');\n  const lines = content.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());\n  results.lines += lines.length;\n  \n  lines.forEach(line => {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(line);\n      const timestamp = data.timestamp;\n      const lineTime = new Date(timestamp).getTime();\n      const hour = timestamp ? timestamp.substring(11, 13) : 'unknown';\n      \n      if (!results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour]) {\n        results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour] = { errors: 0, messages: 0, api429: 0 };\n      }\n      results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].messages++;\n      \n      if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n        results.periods.last30m.lines++;\n      }\n      \n      // Task tracking\n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'user') {\n        const match = JSON.stringify(data.message.content).match(/\\[cron:[^\\s]+\\s+([^\\]]+)\\]/);\n        if (match) {\n          const task = match[1];\n          results.periods.last6h.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last6h.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) {\n            results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n            results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Error analysis\n      if (data.message?.stopReason === 'error') {\n        const errorMsg = data.message.errorMessage || '';\n        results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].errors++;\n        \n        if (errorMsg.includes('429') || errorMsg.includes('速率限制') || errorMsg.includes('访问量过大')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api429++;\n          results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].api429++;\n          \n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) results.periods.last1h.errors.api429++;\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) results.periods.last30m.errors++;\n          \n          if (lastWas429) {\n            consecutive429++;\n            results.patterns.maxConsecutive429 = Math.max(results.patterns.maxConsecutive429, consecutive429);\n          } else {\n            consecutive429 = 1;\n          }\n          lastWas429 = true;\n        } else {\n          lastWas429 = false;\n          consecutive429 = 0;\n        }\n        \n        if (errorMsg.includes('500') || errorMsg.includes('502') || errorMsg.includes('503')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api5xx++;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) results.periods.last1h.errors.api5xx++;\n        }\n        if (errorMsg.includes('400') || errorMsg.includes('参数有误')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api4xx++;\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Tool errors\n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'toolResult') {\n        const resultStr = JSON.stringify(data.message.content);\n        const tool = data.message.toolName;\n        \n        if (resultStr.includes('\"status\":\"error\"') || resultStr.includes('\"error\"')) {\n          if (resultStr.includes('ENOENT')) {\n            results.toolErrors.push({ tool, type: 'file_not_found', time: timestamp });\n          } else if (resultStr.includes('Could not find the exact text')) {\n            results.toolErrors.push({ tool, type: 'edit_not_found', time: timestamp });\n          }\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Process errors\n      if (data.type === 'custom' && data.customType?.includes('error')) {\n        results.processErrors++;\n      }\n      \n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n});\n\n// Peak hours\nresults.patterns.peakHours = Object.entries(results.periods.last6h.hourly)\n  .filter(([h, d]) => d.api429 > 5)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1].api429 - a[1].api429)\n  .map(([h, d]) => ({ hour: h, errors: d.api429 }));\n\nconsole.log('=== Deep Log Analysis (05:54) ===');\nconsole.log(`Time: ${results.scanTime}`);\nconsole.log(`Files: ${results.files}, Lines: ${results.lines}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== 6 Hour Summary ===');\nconsole.log(`429: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api429} (${(results.periods.last6h.errors.api429/6).toFixed(1)}/h)`);\nconsole.log(`5xx: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api5xx}`);\nconsole.log(`4xx: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api4xx}`);\nconsole.log(`Tool Errors: ${results.toolErrors.length}`);\nconsole.log(`Process Errors: ${results.processErrors}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Last 1 Hour ===');\nconsole.log(`429: ${results.periods.last1h.errors.api429}`);\nconsole.log(`5xx: ${results.periods.last1h.errors.api5xx}`);\nconsole.log(`Tasks: ${Object.keys(results.periods.last1h.tasks).length}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Last 30 Minutes ===');\nconsole.log(`Lines: ${results.periods.last30m.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`429 Errors: ${results.periods.last30m.errors}`);\nconsole.log(`Active Tasks: ${Object.keys(results.periods.last30m.tasks).length}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Peak Hours ===');\nresults.patterns.peakHours.slice(0, 5).forEach(p => {\n  console.log(`  ${p.hour}:00 - ${p.errors} errors`);\n});\n\nconsole.log('\\n=== Top Tasks ===');\nObject.entries(results.periods.last6h.tasks)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1])\n  .slice(0, 6)\n  .forEach(([task, count]) => {\n    const rate1h = results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] || 0;\n    console.log(`  ${task}: ${count} (6h) → ${rate1h}/h`);\n  });\n\n// Health score\nconst rate6h = results.periods.last6h.errors.api429 / 6;\nconst rate1h = results.periods.last1h.errors.api429;\nlet health = 10;\nif (rate6h > 10) health -= 1.5;\nif (rate6h > 15) health -= 1;\nif (rate1h > 0) health -= 1;\nif (results.toolErrors.length > 5) health -= 0.5;\nif (rate1h === 0 && rate6h > 10) health += 0.5;\n\nconsole.log(`\\n=== Health Score: ${health}/10 ===`);\n\n// Trend\nconsole.log('\\n=== Trend ===');\nif (rate1h === 0) {\n  console.log('✅ Stable - No 429 errors in last hour');\n} else if (rate1h < rate6h) {\n  console.log('✅ Improving');\n} else {\n  console.log('⚠️ Monitor needed');\n}\n\n// Detect new patterns\nif (results.toolErrors.length > 10) {\n  results.newPatterns.push({\n    id: 'PAT-020',\n    desc: '工具调用失败增加',\n    count: results.toolErrors.length\n  });\n}\n\nif (results.newPatterns.length > 0) {\n  console.log('\\n=== New Patterns Detected ===');\n  results.newPatterns.forEach(p => {\n    console.log(`${p.id}: ${p.desc} (${p.count} times)`);\n  });\n}\n\nfs.writeFileSync('/tmp/an