{"type":"message","id":"dd7d25d3","parentId":"2ed9a3d1","timestamp":"2026-02-24T23:30:01.567Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 7:30 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771975801541}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce5d374b","parentId":"dd7d25d3","timestamp":"2026-02-24T23:31:06.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行深度日志分析任务，当前时间是 2026-02-25 07:30 (Asia/Shanghai)。这是高峰期（07:00-09:00）的中段，需要特别关注错误率。\n\n我需要：\n1. 分析最近 6 小时的日志\n2. 特别关注 429 错误\n3. 生成报告文件\n4. 更新 evolution-history\n5. 如果有新模式，更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n让我执行深度分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ddc2fc4ed98e4050a01fba96","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/deep_analysis_0730.js << 'SCRIPT'\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst sessionsDir = '/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions';\nconst sixHoursAgo = Date.now() - (6 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst oneHourAgo = Date.now() - (60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst thirtyMinAgo = Date.now() - (30 * 60 * 1000);\nconst fifteenMinAgo = Date.now() - (15 * 60 * 1000);\nconst fiveMinAgo = Date.now() - (5 * 60 * 1000);\n\nconst results = {\n  scanTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  files: 0,\n  lines: 0,\n  periods: {\n    last6h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0, api4xx: 0 }, tasks: {}, hourly: {} },\n    last1h: { errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0 }, tasks: {} },\n    last30m: { errors: 0, tasks: {}, lines: 0 },\n    last15m: { errors: 0, tasks: {}, lines: 0 },\n    last5m: { errors: 0, lines: 0 }\n  },\n  peakHours: [],\n  peakProgress: { started: true, elapsed: 30, remaining: 90, nextCritical: 30 },\n  newErrors: [],\n  trends: { improving: false, stable: true, warning: false }\n};\n\nconst files = fs.readdirSync(sessionsDir)\n  .filter(f => f.endsWith('.jsonl'))\n  .map(f => ({\n    path: path.join(sessionsDir, f),\n    mtime: fs.statSync(path.join(sessionsDir, f)).mtime.getTime()\n  }))\n  .filter(f => f.mtime >= sixHoursAgo);\n\nresults.files = files.length;\n\n// Track errors by time window for trend analysis\nlet errorsBy5MinWindow = {};\n\nfiles.forEach(file => {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(file.path, 'utf8');\n  const lines = content.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());\n  results.lines += lines.length;\n  \n  lines.forEach(line => {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(line);\n      const timestamp = data.timestamp;\n      const lineTime = new Date(timestamp).getTime();\n      const hour = timestamp ? timestamp.substring(11, 13) : 'unknown';\n      const minute = timestamp ? parseInt(timestamp.substring(14, 16)) : 0;\n      \n      if (!results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour]) {\n        results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour] = { errors: 0, messages: 0, api429: 0 };\n      }\n      results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].messages++;\n      \n      if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) results.periods.last30m.lines++;\n      if (lineTime >= fifteenMinAgo) results.periods.last15m.lines++;\n      if (lineTime >= fiveMinAgo) results.periods.last5m.lines++;\n      \n      // Task tracking\n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'user') {\n        const match = JSON.stringify(data.message.content).match(/\\[cron:[^\\s]+\\s+([^\\]]+)\\]/);\n        if (match) {\n          const task = match[1];\n          results.periods.last6h.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last6h.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) {\n            results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last1h.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) {\n            results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last30m.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= fifteenMinAgo) {\n            results.periods.last15m.tasks[task] = (results.periods.last15m.tasks[task] || 0) + 1;\n          }\n        }\n      }\n      \n      // Error analysis\n      if (data.message?.stopReason === 'error') {\n        const errorMsg = data.message.errorMessage || '';\n        results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].errors++;\n        \n        if (errorMsg.includes('429') || errorMsg.includes('速率限制') || errorMsg.includes('访问量过大')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api429++;\n          results.periods.last6h.hourly[hour].api429++;\n          \n          // Track by 5-min window for trend\n          const windowKey = `${hour}:${Math.floor(minute / 5) * 5}`;\n          errorsBy5MinWindow[windowKey] = (errorsBy5MinWindow[windowKey] || 0) + 1;\n          \n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) {\n            results.periods.last1h.errors.api429++;\n            results.newErrors.push({ time: timestamp, msg: errorMsg.substring(0, 80) });\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) results.periods.last30m.errors++;\n          if (lineTime >= fifteenMinAgo) results.periods.last15m.errors++;\n          if (lineTime >= fiveMinAgo) results.periods.last5m.errors++;\n        }\n        \n        if (errorMsg.includes('500') || errorMsg.includes('502') || errorMsg.includes('503')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api5xx++;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) results.periods.last1h.errors.api5xx++;\n        }\n        if (errorMsg.includes('400') || errorMsg.includes('参数有误')) {\n          results.periods.last6h.errors.api4xx++;\n        }\n      }\n      \n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n});\n\n// Peak hours\nresults.peakHours = Object.entries(results.periods.last6h.hourly)\n  .filter(([h, d]) => d.api429 > 5)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1].api429 - a[1].api429)\n  .map(([h, d]) => ({ hour: h, errors: d.api429 }));\n\nconsole.log('=== 🔴 PEAK HOUR ANALYSIS (07:30) ===');\nconsole.log(`Time: ${results.scanTime}`);\nconsole.log(`Files: ${results.files}, Lines: ${results.lines}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== 6 Hour Summary ===');\nconsole.log(`429: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api429} (${(results.periods.last6h.errors.api429/6).toFixed(1)}/h)`);\nconsole.log(`5xx: ${results.periods.last6h.errors.api5xx}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== 🔴 Peak Hour Progress ===');\nconsole.log(`Started: 07:00`);\nconsole.log(`Current: 07:30`);\nconsole.log(`Elapsed: 30 minutes`);\nconsole.log(`Remaining: 90 minutes`);\nconsole.log(`Next critical: 08:00 (in 30 min)\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Real-time Monitoring ===');\nconsole.log(`Last 1h 429: ${results.periods.last1h.errors.api429}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 30m 429: ${results.periods.last30m.errors}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 15m 429: ${results.periods.last15m.errors}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 5m 429: ${results.periods.last5m.errors}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Activity Levels ===');\nconsole.log(`Last 30m lines: ${results.periods.last30m.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 15m lines: ${results.periods.last15m.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 5m lines: ${results.periods.last5m.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 30m tasks: ${Object.keys(results.periods.last30m.tasks).length}`);\nconsole.log(`Last 15m tasks: ${Object.keys(results.periods.last15m.tasks).length}\\n`);\n\nconsole.log('=== Historical Peak Hours ===');\nresults.peakHours.forEach(p => {\n  const marker = p.hour === '07' || p.hour === '08' || p.hour === '09' ? '🔴' : '  ';\n  const current = p.hour === '07' ? ' ← CURRENT' : '';\n  console.log(`${marker} ${p.hour}:00 - ${p.errors} errors${current}`);\n});\n\n// New errors\nif (results.newErrors.length > 0) {\n  console.log('\\n=== ⚠️ NEW 429 ERRORS IN LAST HOUR ===');\n  results.newErrors.slice(0, 10).forEach((e, i) => {\n    console.log(`[${i + 1}] ${e.time}: ${e.msg}`);\n  });\n  results.trends.warning = true;\n  results.trends.stable = false;\n}\n\nconsole.log('\\n=== Top Tasks (30m) ===');\nObject.entries(results.periods.last30m.tasks)\n  .sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1])\n  .slice(0, 6)\n  .forEach(([task, count]) => {\n    console.log(`  ${task}: ${count}/30m`);\n  });\n\n// Health score\nconst rate6h = results.periods.last6h.errors.api429 / 6;\nconst rate30m = results.periods.last30m.errors * 2;\nconst rate15m = results.periods.last15m.errors * 4;\nconst rate5m = results.periods.last5m.errors * 12;\n\nlet health = 10;\nif (rate6h > 10) health -= 1;\nif (rate6h > 15) health -= 0.5;\nif (rate30m > 5) health -= 2;\nif (rate15m > 5) health -= 1;\nif (rate5m > 0) health -= 1;\nif (rate30m === 0 && rate15m === 0) health += 0.5; // Bonus for stability\n\nconsole.log(`\\n=== Health Score: ${health}/10 ===`);\nconsole.log(`30m rate: ${rate30m}/h | 15m rate: ${rate15m}/h | 5m rate: ${rate5m}/h`);\n\n// Trend analysis\nconsole.log('\\n=== Trend Analysis ===');\nif (results.periods.last30m.errors === 0) {\n  console.log('✅ Stable - Peak hour progressing without errors');\n  console.log('✅ System handling load well');\n  results.trends.stable = true;\n} else if (results.periods.last15m.errors < results.periods.last30m.errors / 2) {\n  console.log('✅ Improving - Error rate decreasing');\n  results.trends.improving = true;\n  results.trends.stable = false;\n} else {\n  console.log('⚠️ Warning - Errors detected, monitor closely');\n  results.trends.warning = true;\n  results.trends.stable = false;\n}\n\n// 08:00 warning\nconsole.log('\\n=== ⚠️ 08:00 Approaching ===');\nconsole.log('Historical data: 38 errors at 08:00 (highest)');\nconsole.log('Time to 08:00: 30 minutes');\nconsole.log('Recommendation: Continue monitoring, prepare for potential spike');\n\nfs.writeFileSync('/tmp/analysis_0730.json', JSON.stringify(results, null, 2));\nSCRIPT\n\nnode /tmp/deep_analysis_0730.js","timeout":120,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":109953,"output":2622,"cacheRead":10176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122751,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771975801558}}
