{"type":"message","id":"547afc37","parentId":"e3ad0415","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:02:32.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我已经成功更新了 pattern-registry.md，添加了 PAT-020 和 PAT-021。现在让我生成最终的分析报告。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 深度日志分析完成 (12:00)\n\n### 系统状态\n\n| 指标 | 数值 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 健康评分 | **8/10** | ⚠️ |\n| 6h 429 错误 | 13 次 (2.2/h) | ⚠️ |\n| **问题时段** | **03:00** | 🔴 |\n| 5xx/4xx 错误 | 0 次 | ✅ |\n\n### 🔴 P1 问题：03:00 时段 429 错误\n\n**发现**: 03:00-04:00 时段集中出现 13 次 429 错误\n\n**根本原因**:\n1. GLM-5 API 在 03:00 时段可能有限制\n2. 多个 cron 任务在该时段并发\n3. API 配额较低\n\n**影响**: 6 小时健康评分降至 8/10\n\n### 📝 改进建议\n\n| 优先级 | 建议 | 预期效果 |\n|--------|------|----------|\n| **P1** | 跳过 03:00 时段的非关键任务 | 减少并发冲突 |\n| **P2** | 实现智能调度（高峰期降频） | 预防未来问题 |\n\n### 🎯 立即行动\n\n**建议**: 在下一个 03:00 时段前调整 cron 配置：\n- `evolver-log-analysis`: 跳过 03:00\n- `evomap-auto-bounty`: 降低频率\n\n### 生成的文件\n\n- ✅ 报告: `memory/log-analysis-2026-02-25-1200.md`\n- ✅ Round: `evolver_history/.../round-204-2026-02-25-1200.md`\n- ✅ Pattern: **PAT-021** 已注册（03:00 时段 429 错误）\n\n### 总结\n\n系统当前运行正常，但发现 **03:00 时段** 存在 429 错误集中问题，需要调整调度策略。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":538,"output":499,"cacheRead":125248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771992124382}}
{"type":"message","id":"078ceddc","parentId":"547afc37","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:30:00.636Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 12:30 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771993800628}}
{"type":"message","id":"e76b29ae","parentId":"078ceddc","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:30:45.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"系统要求我执行深度日志分析任务。我需要：\n1. 分析最近6小时的日志\n2. 查找错误模式\n3. 生成报告文件\n4. 更新 evolution-history\n5. 如果有新模式，更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n让我执行分析脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bd83c2476e6c4c468115240c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/analysis_1230.js << 'SCRIPT'\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst sessionsDir = '/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions';\nconst sixHoursAgo = Date.now() - (6 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst oneHourAgo = Date.now() - (60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst thirtyMinAgo = Date.now() - (30 * 60 * 1000);\n\nconst results = {\n  scanTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  files: 0, lines: 0,\n  errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0, api4xx: 0 },\n  periods: { last1h: 0, last30m: 0 },\n  hourly: {},\n  recent: [],\n  tasks: {},\n  trend: ''\n};\n\nconst files = fs.readdirSync(sessionsDir)\n  .filter(f => f.endsWith('.jsonl'))\n  .map(f => ({ path: path.join(sessionsDir, f), mtime: fs.statSync(path.join(sessionsDir, f)).mtime.getTime() }))\n  .filter(f => f.mtime >= sixHoursAgo);\n\nresults.files = files.length;\n\nlet lastErrorTime = null;\n\nfiles.forEach(file => {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(file.path, 'utf8');\n  const lines = content.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());\n  results.lines += lines.length;\n  \n  lines.forEach(line => {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(line);\n      const ts = data.timestamp;\n      const lineTime = new Date(ts).getTime();\n      const hour = ts ? ts.substring(11, 13) : '??';\n      \n      if (!results.hourly[hour]) results.hourly[hour] = { errors: 0, api429: 0, messages: 0 };\n      results.hourly[hour].messages++;\n      \n      if (data.type === 'message' && data.message?.role === 'user') {\n        const m = JSON.stringify(data.message.content).match(/\\[cron:[^\\s]+\\s+([^\\]]+)\\]/);\n        if (m) results.tasks[m[1]] = (results.tasks[m[1]] || 0) + 1;\n      }\n      \n      if (data.message?.stopReason === 'error') {\n        const msg = data.message.errorMessage || '';\n        results.hourly[hour].errors++;\n        \n        if (msg.includes('429') || msg.includes('速率') || msg.includes('访问量过大')) {\n          results.errors.api429++;\n          results.hourly[hour].api429++;\n          lastErrorTime = lineTime;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) {\n            results.periods.last1h++;\n            if (results.recent.length < 5) results.recent.push({ time: ts, msg: msg.substring(0, 60) });\n          }\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) results.periods.last30m++;\n        }\n        if (msg.includes('500') || msg.includes('502') || msg.includes('503')) results.errors.api5xx++;\n        if (msg.includes('400') || msg.includes('参数有误')) results.errors.api4xx++;\n      }\n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n});\n\n// Calculate time since last error\nconst minsSinceError = lastErrorTime ? Math.floor((Date.now() - lastErrorTime) / 60000) : 360;\n\nconsole.log('=== Log Analysis (12:30) ===');\nconsole.log(`Time: ${results.scanTime}`);\nconsole.log(`Files: ${results.files}, Lines: ${results.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`429 (6h): ${results.errors.api429}, (1h): ${results.periods.last1h}, (30m): ${results.periods.last30m}`);\nconsole.log(`5xx: ${results.errors.api5xx}, 4xx: ${results.errors.api4xx}`);\nconsole.log(`Minutes since last error: ${minsSinceError}`);\n\nconsole.log('\\n=== Hourly Distribution ===');\nObject.entries(results.hourly).sort((a,b) => b[1].api429 - a[1].api429).slice(0,5)\n  .forEach(([h,d]) => console.log(`  ${h}:00 - ${d.api429} errors, ${d.messages} msgs`));\n\nif (results.recent.length > 0) {\n  console.log('\\n=== Recent Errors ===');\n  results.recent.forEach((e,i) => console.log(`[${i+1}] ${e.time}: ${e.msg}`));\n}\n\n// Health score calculation\nlet health = 10;\nif (results.errors.api429 > 10) health -= 1;\nif (results.periods.last1h > 0) health -= 1;\nif (results.periods.last1h > 5) health -= 1;\nif (minsSinceError > 60) health += 0.5; // Bonus for stability\n\nconsole.log(`\\n=== Health Score: ${health}/10 ===`);\n\n// Trend\nif (results.periods.last1h === 0 && results.periods.last30m === 0) {\n  results.trend = 'stable';\n  console.log('✅ Trend: Stable - No recent errors');\n} else if (results.periods.last30m === 0) {\n  results.trend = 'improving';\n  console.log('✅ Trend: Improving - Errors in past hour but not recent');\n} else {\n  results.trend = 'monitoring';\n  console.log('⚠️ Trend: Monitoring - Recent errors detected');\n}\n\nfs.writeFileSync('/tmp/analysis_1230.json', JSON.stringify(results, null, 2));\nSCRIPT\n\nnode /tmp/analysis_1230.js","timeout":60,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":116225,"output":1313,"cacheRead":10176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127714,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771993800634}}
