{"type":"message","id":"28d00247","parentId":"0567c641","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:00:00.791Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 1:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771995600776}}
{"type":"message","id":"440637b1","parentId":"28d00247","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:00:37.083Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在 13:00 又执行了一次日志分析。我需要快速检查最近的错误情况，看看 12:50-12:54 时段的错误是否还在持续。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_98488f8dc9644bcd864c3ab4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/analysis_1300.js << 'SCRIPT'\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst sessionsDir = '/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions';\nconst sixHoursAgo = Date.now() - (6 * 60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst oneHourAgo = Date.now() - (60 * 60 * 1000);\nconst thirtyMinAgo = Date.now() - (30 * 60 * 1000);\nconst fiveMinAgo = Date.now() - (5 * 60 * 1000);\n\nconst results = {\n  scanTime: new Date().toISOString(),\n  files: 0, lines: 0,\n  errors: { api429: 0, api5xx: 0 },\n  periods: { last1h: 0, last30m: 0, last5m: 0 },\n  hourly: {},\n  minsSinceError: 360\n};\n\nconst files = fs.readdirSync(sessionsDir)\n  .filter(f => f.endsWith('.jsonl'))\n  .map(f => ({ path: path.join(sessionsDir, f), mtime: fs.statSync(path.join(sessionsDir, f)).mtime.getTime() }))\n  .filter(f => f.mtime >= sixHoursAgo);\n\nresults.files = files.length;\n\nlet lastErrorTime = null;\n\nfiles.forEach(file => {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(file.path, 'utf8');\n  const lines = content.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());\n  results.lines += lines.length;\n  \n  lines.forEach(line => {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(line);\n      const ts = data.timestamp;\n      const lineTime = new Date(ts).getTime();\n      const hour = ts ? ts.substring(11, 13) : '??';\n      \n      if (!results.hourly[hour]) results.hourly[hour] = { errors: 0, api429: 0 };\n      \n      if (data.message?.stopReason === 'error') {\n        const msg = data.message.errorMessage || '';\n        results.hourly[hour].errors++;\n        \n        if (msg.includes('429') || msg.includes('速率') || msg.includes('访问量过大')) {\n          results.errors.api429++;\n          results.hourly[hour].api429++;\n          lastErrorTime = lineTime;\n          if (lineTime >= oneHourAgo) results.periods.last1h++;\n          if (lineTime >= thirtyMinAgo) results.periods.last30m++;\n          if (lineTime >= fiveMinAgo) results.periods.last5m++;\n        }\n        if (msg.includes('500') || msg.includes('502') || msg.includes('503')) results.errors.api5xx++;\n      }\n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n});\n\nresults.minsSinceError = lastErrorTime ? Math.floor((Date.now() - lastErrorTime) / 60000) : 360;\n\nconsole.log('=== Log Analysis (13:00) ===');\nconsole.log(`Files: ${results.files}, Lines: ${results.lines}`);\nconsole.log(`429 (6h): ${results.errors.api429}`);\nconsole.log(`429 (1h): ${results.periods.last1h}, (30m): ${results.periods.last30m}, (5m): ${results.periods.last5m}`);\nconsole.log(`Minutes since last error: ${results.minsSinceError}`);\n\n// Health score\nlet health = 10;\nif (results.errors.api429 > 10) health -= 0.5;\nif (results.periods.last30m > 0) health -= 0.5;\nif (results.periods.last5m > 0) health -= 1;\nif (results.periods.last5m === 0 && results.periods.last30m === 0) health += 0.5;\n\nconsole.log(`\\nHealth: ${health}/10`);\n\n// Trend\nif (results.periods.last5m === 0 && results.periods.last30m === 0) {\n  console.log('✅ Stable - No recent errors');\n} else if (results.periods.last5m === 0) {\n  console.log('✅ Improving - Errors stopped in last 5m');\n} else {\n  console.log('⚠️ Monitoring - Recent errors detected');\n}\n\nfs.writeFileSync('/tmp/analysis_1300.json', JSON.stringify(results, null, 2));\nSCRIPT\n\nnode /tmp/analysis_1300.js","timeout":60,"workdir":"/root/.openclaw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":5884,"output":1007,"cacheRead":130624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137515,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771995600785}}
